=== 鎖定方式 ===
不同生產商採用了不同的鎖定方式，常見的分別為：

* '''鎖定退彈口'''：在將手槍插入槍套時以機械方式鎖定在退彈口，拔槍時需按下對應釋放鈕。採用此方式的包括且不限於：
**'''Safariland ALS'''：被採用為[[美军|美軍]][[SIG_P320手槍|MHS]]的槍套<ref>{{Cite web|title=Safariland ALS holsters|url=https://www.milspecmonkey.com/weapons-page/holsters/447-safariland-als-holsters|accessdate=2020-11-21|author=|date=2014-07-15|format=|work=www.milspecmonkey.com|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210823031031/https://www.milspecmonkey.com/weapons-page/holsters/447-safariland-als-holsters|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":6">{{Cite web|title=Here’s Who’s Supplying the Holsters for the Army M17, M18 Pistols|url=https://www.tactical-life.com/news/army-m17-m18-pistols/|accessdate=2020-11-21|author=TACTICAL-LIFE|date=2018-08-03|format=|publisher=TACTICAL-LIFE|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125100214/https://www.tactical-life.com/news/army-m17-m18-pistols/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":7">{{Cite web|title=US soldiers set to receive new holster as Army deploys its latest pistol|url=https://www.foxnews.com/tech/us-soldiers-set-to-receive-new-holster-as-army-deploys-its-latest-pistol|accessdate=2020-11-21|date=2017-12-18|last=Barrie|first=Allison|work=Fox News|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114234150/https://www.foxnews.com/tech/us-soldiers-set-to-receive-new-holster-as-army-deploys-its-latest-pistol|dead-url=no}}</ref>
**'''Radar L.E.P'''：被採用為英軍[[格洛克17|L131A1]]的槍套<ref>{{Cite web|title=RADAR 1957 new holsters for 2017|url=https://www.gunsweek.com/en/accessories/shot-show/radar-1957-new-holsters-2017|accessdate=2020-11-21|author=|date=2017-01-27|format=|work=GUNSweek.com|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125192350/https://www.gunsweek.com/en/accessories/shot-show/radar-1957-new-holsters-2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* '''鎖定扳機護弓'''：在將手槍插入槍套時以機械方式鎖定在扳機護弓，拔槍時需按下對應釋放鈕。採用此方式的包括且不限於：
**'''Blackhawk SERPA'''：被採用為美軍[[貝瑞塔M9手槍|M9]]的槍套<ref>{{Cite web|title=U.S. Army Adopts Blackhawk SERPA Tactical Holster|url=https://www.tactical-life.com/news/u-s-army-adopts-blackhawk-serpa-tactical-holster/|accessdate=2020-11-21|author=TACTICAL-LIFE|date=2014-01-13|format=|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129133154/https://www.tactical-life.com/news/u-s-army-adopts-blackhawk-serpa-tactical-holster/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於SERPA槍套的操作危險性較大、物料較差令槍套可被破壞性拔離用家、碎屑進入後會把手槍卡死、部分手槍在坐姿會在用家不知情下被槍套壓下彈匣釋放鈕等<ref name=":9">{{Cite web|title=KNOWN ISSUES WITH SERPA HOLSTERS|url=http://tagtrainingllc.bympa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Safety-Issues-Re-Serpa.pdf|accessdate=2020-11-21|author=Tactical Analysis Group|date=|format=pdf|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111193255/http://tagtrainingllc.bympa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Safety-Issues-Re-Serpa.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因此SERPA槍套已被[[洛杉矶警察局|洛杉磯警察局]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=LAPD Bans Use Of Blackhawk SERPA Holster for Safety Reasons|url=https://lockedback.com/lapd-bans-use-blackhawk-serpa-holster/|accessdate=2020-11-21|date=2017-06-24|work=Locked Back|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110022803/https://lockedback.com/lapd-bans-use-blackhawk-serpa-holster/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、所有聯邦執法訓練中心<ref>{{Cite web|title=EXECUTIVE SUMMARY AND DECISION|url=https://www.fletc.gov/sites/default/files/imported_files/reference/public-information/freedom-of-information-act-foia/reading-room/training-information/holisterStudy.pdf|accessdate=2020-11-23|author=Homeland Security|date=|format=pdf|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118004004/https://www.fletc.gov/sites/default/files/imported_files/reference/public-information/freedom-of-information-act-foia/reading-room/training-information/holisterStudy.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>及不同民營射擊訓練場<ref name=":9" />禁止使用，而美軍在更換新手槍後亦沒有繼續採用。
**'''AFV Club 執法者II'''：被採用為[[中華民國警察|中華民國警察]]的[[瓦爾特PPQ半自動手槍|PPQ M2 NPA]]槍套<ref name=":8">{{Cite web|title=防歹徒正面奪槍 台南警將換3226把PPQ新槍安全升級 - 社會|url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2461861|accessdate=2020-11-21|author=|date=2018-06-18|last=自由時報電子報|format=|work=自由時報電子報|publisher=|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129132905/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2461861|dead-url=no}}</ref>，及[[中華民國國軍|中華民國國軍]]的[[T75手槍|T75K3]]槍套<ref>{{Cite web|title=致命缺陷？國造新槍爆烏龍設計 繫上槍繩就無法換彈匣|url=https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4769204|accessdate=2021-02-18|date=2020-08-10|last=聯合新聞網|work=聯合新聞網|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2020-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013141715/https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4769204|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=45手槍老舊又笨重！海軍汰換將買1442把T75K3手槍|url=https://www.nownews.com/news/5053022|accessdate=2021-02-18|date=2020-09-01|last=NOWnews今日新聞|work=NOWnews今日新聞|language=zh-TW}}</ref>。部份警員因對配發槍套無信心而自購槍套。
**'''Safariland GLS'''
* '''鎖定武器燈'''：在將手槍插入槍套時以機械方式鎖定在武器燈，拔槍時需按下對應釋放鈕。此類槍套由於以武器燈為鎖定方式，因此同一槍套可用於多種手槍，且不受瞄具、抑制器等影響。採用此方式的包括且不限於：
**'''[[SureFire|SureFire]] MasterFire快速部署槍套'''：鎖定武器燈燈頭，必須使用特別設計的XH系列武器燈<ref>{{Cite web|title=Review: SureFire MasterFire Rapid-Deploy Holster|url=https://www.shootingillustrated.com/articles/2017/11/25/review-surefire-masterfire-rapid-deploy-holster/|accessdate=2020-08-12|work=www.shootingillustrated.com|language=en|dead-url=no|archive-date=2018-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180305113250/https://www.shootingillustrated.com/articles/2017/11/25/review-surefire-masterfire-rapid-deploy-holster/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Surefire Masterfire Holster with x300 Weaponlight - Review -|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2017/06/23/surefire-masterfire-x300/|accessdate=2020-08-12|date=2017-06-23|work=The Firearm Blog|language=en-US|dead-url=no|archive-date=2018-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627181122/http://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2017/06/23/surefire-masterfire-x300/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=SureFire tiptoes into tactical holster market with Masterfire holster system :|url=https://www.guns.com/news/2017/06/01/surefire-masterfire-holster-system|accessdate=2020-08-20|work=Guns.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210627021918/https://www.guns.com/news/2017/06/01/surefire-masterfire-holster-system|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
**'''Blackhawk Omnivore'''：可鎖定SureFire X300或Streamlight TLR-1尺寸武器燈，亦可直接鎖定手槍的底部導軌<ref>{{Cite web|title=Review: Hands-on with the Blackhawk Omnivore holster|url=https://taskandpurpose.com/reviews/blackhawk-omnivore-holster-review/|access-date=2021-10-08|author=Travis Pike|date=2021-09-22|work=Task & Purpose|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211216091422/https://taskandpurpose.com/reviews/blackhawk-omnivore-holster-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
**'''被動鎖定'''：除上述兩款槍套，市場上亦有如T.REX Arms RagnarokSD、PHLster Floodlight等同樣鎖定武器燈、但無額外鎖定系統的KYDEX槍套<ref>{{Cite web|title=Modern Holsters: Carrying into the Future|url=https://www.recoilweb.com/modern-holsters-carrying-into-the-future-168196.html|access-date=2021-10-08|date=2021-06-11|last=Keel|first=Tamara|work=Recoil|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211009161751/https://www.recoilweb.com/modern-holsters-carrying-into-the-future-168196.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*'''翻蓋式'''：在將手槍插入槍套後手動翻動上蓋，拔槍時需按下上蓋的按鈕並向前推開<ref>{{Cite web|title=How to Draw From a Safariland SLS Holster|url=http://modernserviceweapons.com/?p=14945|accessdate=2020-11-21|author=Tim Lau|date=2015-04-09|format=|publisher=Modern Service Weapons|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129094155/http://modernserviceweapons.com/?p=14945|dead-url=no}}</ref>。採用此方式的包括且不限於：
**'''Safariland SLS'''：被[[陸上自衛隊|陸上自衛隊]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=平成22年5月16日　陸上自衛隊新発田駐屯地創設57周年記念行事　その２ {{!}} 日本警察特殊部隊愛好会（JP-SWAT / Japan Police Special Weapons And Tactics）|url=http://jp-swat.com/report/jsdf/100516_b.html|accessdate=2020-11-21|author=|date=2010-05-16|format=|work=jp-swat.com|publisher=|language=ja|archive-date=2016-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160706063527/http://jp-swat.com/report/jsdf/100516_b.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[美国海军陆战队|美國海軍陸戰隊]]等軍警單位廣泛採用<ref>{{Cite web|title=MARSOC M45A1 Contract Holsters from Safariland|url=http://modernserviceweapons.com/?p=4275|accessdate=2020-11-21|author=Tim Lau|date=2013-08-25|format=|publisher=Modern Service Weapons|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190224075417/http://modernserviceweapons.com/?p=4275|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並被美軍採用為MHS槍套的第三級鎖定<ref name=":6" /><ref name=":7" />
**'''G-Code XST'''<ref>{{Cite web|title=REVIEW: G Code XST Holster|url=https://copperstar.wordpress.com/2014/05/20/review/|accessdate=2020-11-23|date=2014-05-20|work=CopperStar|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118150337/https://copperstar.wordpress.com/2014/05/20/review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* '''改變拔槍動作'''：拔槍時需以傾斜手槍等方式解鎖。採用此方式的包括中華民國警察的[[史密斯威森M39手槍|5904]]槍套，但在警察與犯人近距離接觸時有容易被奪槍的危險<ref name=":8" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=警槍遭搶案例多 資深警建議修改執勤方式|url=https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20180617/2Z562B3NGW4OQGJILN7HOPJF7Q/|accessdate=2020-11-21|author=|date=2018-06-17|format=|work=蘋果新聞網|publisher=|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129010909/https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20180617/2Z562B3NGW4OQGJILN7HOPJF7Q/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。部份警員因對配發槍套無信心而自購槍套<ref>{{Cite web|title=警跌倒遭通緝犯奪槍 「新舊槍套」皆有2道防搶裝置|url=https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=393134|accessdate=2021-03-29|date=2018-06-17|last=三立新聞網|work=www.setn.com|language=zh-TW}}</ref>。
